column1631:
24/Feb/25 12:55 AM;jim.ren@hp.com;[~michal.szatkowski@hp.com] 
 # Should the app display separate FW update info for the headset and charge stand (just like eg. VFree 60+ UC)? Even if CS is not docked?
{color:#FF0000}we should display the separate FW update info for HS and FW, same as eg. Legend 50/30 and charger case.{color}
 # Is it possible for the user to initiate DFU only for charge stand (when docked)?
{color:#FF0000}The CS and HS paired with BLE, only HS can Dfu the CS, but user can choose which one to be dfu'd, just like Legend 50/30 and charger case, no matter the HS is docked or not, as long as they are paired.{color}
 # Is it a way to utilize any other device (eg. peregrine cs) to mimic the falcon cs for discovery and testing purposes?
{color:#FF0000}No, the peregrine CS is another platform product and doesn't support BLE, so it can't be paired with the falcon HS.{color};;;

