column34:
h2. ANC/T Multipoint in-call support when connected to BT700 (desktop/laptop) and mobile Phone 
Note: Implement Scenario described in epic & [GitHub > Wiki > ANC & Transparency Features|https://github.azc.ext.hp.com/Poly-Lens-Apps/Lens-App-iOS/wiki/ANC-&-Transparency-Features]

h3. 2. Multipoint connection with BT700 and Phone
 * *Given* the headset is connected to a mobile phone via bluetooth
 ** *And* the Lens Mobile app shows the headset {{connected}}
 ** *And* the same headset is also connected to the BT700 attached to a desktop/laptop computer
 ** *And* the Lens Desktop app is showing the headset {{connected}}
 ** *And* the Teams client is in an Active call
 ** *And* the Lens Mobile app ANC=Adaptive feature is Active {{On}} and Transparency feature is Inactive {{Off}}
 * *When* the user tries to toggle the Transparency feature active {{On}}
 * *Then* the Lens Mobile app pops up a dialog saying that the feature is not available during a call (check Figma for correct message)

